The United States has indicated its support for Turkey's position.
Karzai said on 5 May that Turkey's concern that its troops would be involved in the renewed turmoil in Afghanistan is redundant.
He also indicated, however, that the Afghan government would accept any decision taken by the countries participating in the peacekeeping force.
